<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV63">
<l>vaṇṇañ civantuḷa vāṉā ṭamaruṅ kuḷirviḻiya</l>
<l>taṇmeṉ kamalat taṭampōl polintaṉa tāmivaiyō</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉ tirumā tirumukan taṉṉoṭuṅ kātalceytēṟ</l>
<l>keṇṇam pukuntaṭi yēṉoṭik kāla mirukkiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With cool eyes that reside in the heavenly land, that are reddened in colour,</l>
<l>they have flourished like tanks of cool soft lotuses. As for these,</l>
<l>– having entered into concern for me who is in love with the holy mouth of Tirumāl,</l>
<l>Kaṇṇaṉ, this time they will stay with me who am [his] servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
